Holger Eggerichs:

"OPEN STANDARDS are technologies, processes and content, that are made available to the
general public and are developed and maintained in a collaborative and consent driven
process. We intend to use open standards in order to support the interoperability of
commons and the widespread of relevant knowledge to foster large scale adoption."


